# Local Rust build artifacts
rust/target/
rust/settings.json

# Local binary/package artifacts
*.exe
*.scr
*.msi
*.pdb

# Overlay assets are local-only by default
assets/overlays/*
!assets/overlays/README.md
# matrisaver-default.png is the tracked, shippable default overlay —
# a copy of the project's own brand mark (assets/branding/logo.png),
# owned outright, zero third-party rights. Counter-ignored so it
# survives clones and ships in the installer. Every other image in
# this directory (film stills, stock vectors, WhatsApp photos, etc.)
# stays local-only by design — those carry third-party copyright the
# MIT license cannot grant.
!assets/overlays/matrisaver-default.png

# Source-resolution branding assets (4K PNG / 6K JPG from OpenArt) stay
# local; only the downscaled web variants in assets/branding/ are tracked.
assets/assets/

# Runtime/validation artifacts are local-only by default.
artifacts/*
!artifacts/readme.md
